room_title: Escape room "Blood of the Original" by Keystone Escape Games in Reno
room_description: Your team will be participating in an High energy and exciting escape room adventure. In which Eccentric collector Alcott Morriston has stolen he Blood of the Original Vampire that granted you and your coven the strength and eternal life. As Honorary members of the house of Baloga, a dynasty of Vampires who have called Europe home for centuries, You have been tasked with the duty of recovering the Blood of the Original.
